dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Russell Perry. May I have your name, please?
Hi Russell, my name is Abigail Lee.
Nice to meet you, Abigail. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's one two three four five.
Thank you. And may I also have your date of birth for verification purposes?
My date of birth is January five, nineteen ninety-eight.
Great, thank you for providing that information, Abigail. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today regarding your policy?
I would like to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can help you with that. Let's go ahead and get the details of your new vehicle.
Thank you for your time, Abigail. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
